[{"text": "I'm here today to share with you", "start": 16.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "an extraordinary journey -", "start": 18.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "extraordinarily rewarding journey,\nactually -", "start": 20.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "which brought me into", "start": 23.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "training rats", "start": 25.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to save human lives", "start": 27.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "by detecting landmines", "start": 29.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and tuberculosis.", "start": 31.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "As a child, I had two passions.", "start": 33.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "One was a passion for rodents.", "start": 36.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I had all kinds of rats,", "start": 39.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "mice, hamsters,", "start": 41.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "gerbils, squirrels.", "start": 43.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "You name it, I bred it, and I sold them to pet shops.", "start": 45.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "(Laughter)", "start": 48.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I also had a passion for Africa.", "start": 50.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Growing up in a multicultural environment,", "start": 53.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we had African students in the house,", "start": 55.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and I learned about their stories,", "start": 57.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "so different backgrounds,", "start": 59.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "dependency on imported know-how,", "start": 61.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "goods, services,", "start": 64.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "exuberant cultural diversity.", "start": 66.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Africa was truly fascinating for me.", "start": 69.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I became an industrial engineer,", "start": 71.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "engineer in product development,", "start": 73.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and I focused on appropriate detection technologies,", "start": 75.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "actually the first appropriate technologies", "start": 78.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "for developing countries.", "start": 80.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I started working in the industry,", "start": 83.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "but I wasn't really happy to contribute", "start": 85.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to a material consumer society", "start": 87.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "in a linear, extracting", "start": 90.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and manufacturing mode.", "start": 93.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I quit my job to focus on the real world problem:", "start": 95.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "landmines.", "start": 97.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "We're talking '95 now.", "start": 100.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Princess Diana is announcing on TV", "start": 103.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that landmines form a structural barrier", "start": 106.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to any development, which is really true.", "start": 108.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "As long as these devices are there,", "start": 111.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "or there is suspicion of landmines,", "start": 113.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "you can't really enter into the land.", "start": 115.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Actually, there was an appeal worldwide", "start": 117.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "for new detectors", "start": 119.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "sustainable in the environments", "start": 122.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "where they're needed to produce,", "start": 124.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "which is mainly in the developing world.", "start": 126.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "We chose rats.", "start": 128.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Why would you choose rats?", "start": 130.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Because, aren't they vermin?", "start": 132.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Well, actually rats are,", "start": 134.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in contrary to what most people think about them,", "start": 136.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "rats are highly sociable creatures.", "start": 138.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "And actually, our product -- what you see here.", "start": 142.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "There's a target somewhere here.", "start": 145.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "You see an operator, a trained African", "start": 147.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "with his rats in front", "start": 149.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "who actually are left and right.", "start": 151.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "There, the animal finds a mine.", "start": 153.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "It scratches on the soil.", "start": 155.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And the animal comes back for a food reward.", "start": 157.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Very, very simple.", "start": 160.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Very sustainable in this environment.", "start": 162.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Here, the animal gets its food reward.", "start": 165.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And that's how it works.", "start": 168.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Very, very simple.", "start": 170.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Now why would you use rats?", "start": 172.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Rats have been used since the '50s last century,", "start": 174.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in all kinds of experiments.", "start": 176.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Rats have more genetic material", "start": 179.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "allocated to olfaction", "start": 182.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "than any other mammal species.", "start": 184.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "They're extremely sensitive to smell.", "start": 186.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Moreover, they have the mechanisms to map all these smells", "start": 189.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and to communicate about it.", "start": 192.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Now how do we communicate with rats?", "start": 195.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Well don't talk rat,", "start": 197.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "but we have a clicker,", "start": 200.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "a standard method for animal training,", "start": 202.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "which you see there.", "start": 204.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "A clicker, which makes a particular sound", "start": 206.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "with which you can reinforce particular behaviors.", "start": 209.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "First of all, we associate the click sound with a food reward,", "start": 212.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "which is smashed banana and peanuts together in a syringe.", "start": 215.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Once the animal knows click, food,", "start": 219.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "click, food, click, food --", "start": 221.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "so click is food --", "start": 223.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we bring it in a cage with a hole,", "start": 225.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and actually the animal learns", "start": 227.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to stick the nose in the hole", "start": 229.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "under which a target scent is placed,", "start": 231.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and to do that for five seconds --", "start": 233.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "five seconds, which is long for a rat.", "start": 235.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Once the animal knows this, we make the task a bit more difficult.", "start": 237.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "It learns how to find the target smell", "start": 240.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "in a cage with several holes, up to 10 holes.", "start": 243.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Then the animal learns", "start": 246.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to walk on a leash in the open", "start": 248.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and find targets.", "start": 250.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "In the next step, animals learn", "start": 252.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "to find real mines in real minefields.", "start": 255.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "They are tested and accredited", "start": 257.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "according to International Mine Action Standards,", "start": 260.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "just like dogs have to pass a test.", "start": 262.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "This consists of 400 square meters.", "start": 265.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "There's a number of mines", "start": 267.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "placed blindly,", "start": 270.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and the team of trainer and their rat", "start": 272.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "have to find all the targets.", "start": 275.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "If the animal does that, it gets a license", "start": 279.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "as an accredited animal", "start": 282.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to be operational in the field --", "start": 284.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "just like dogs, by the way.", "start": 286.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Maybe one slight difference:", "start": 288.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we can train rats at a fifth of the price", "start": 290.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "of training the mining dog.", "start": 293.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "This is our team in Mozambique:", "start": 295.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "one Tanzanian trainer,", "start": 297.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "who transfers the skills", "start": 299.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to these three Mozambican fellows.", "start": 301.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And you should see the pride in the eyes of these people.", "start": 303.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "They have a skill,", "start": 306.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "which makes them much less dependent", "start": 308.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "on foreign aid.", "start": 310.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Moreover, this small team", "start": 312.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "together with, of course, you need the heavy vehicles", "start": 315.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and the manual de-miners to follow-up.", "start": 318.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "But with this small investment in a rat capacity,", "start": 321.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "we have demonstrated in Mozambique", "start": 324.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that we can reduce the cost-price per square meter", "start": 327.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "up to 60 percent", "start": 330.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of what is currently normal --", "start": 332.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "two dollars per square meter, we do it at $1.18,", "start": 334.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and we can still bring that price down.", "start": 336.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Question of scale.", "start": 338.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "If you can bring in more rats,", "start": 340.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we can actually make the output even bigger.", "start": 342.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "We have a demonstration site in Mozambique.", "start": 344.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Eleven African governments", "start": 347.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "have seen that they can become less dependent", "start": 350.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "by using this technology.", "start": 353.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "They have signed the pact for peace", "start": 355.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and treaty in the Great Lakes region,", "start": 357.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and they endorse hero rats", "start": 360.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "to clear their common borders of landmines.", "start": 363.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "But let me bring you to a very different problem.", "start": 366.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And there's about 6,000 people last year", "start": 369.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that walked on a landmine,", "start": 371.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "but worldwide last year,", "start": 373.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "almost 1.9 million died from tuberculosis", "start": 375.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "as a first cause of infection.", "start": 377.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Especially in Africa", "start": 381.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "where T.B. and HIV are strongly linked,", "start": 383.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "there is a huge common problem.", "start": 386.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "Microscopy, the standard WHO procedure,", "start": 391.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "reaches from 40 to 60 percent reliability.", "start": 394.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "In Tanzania -- the numbers don't lie --", "start": 398.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "45 percent of people -- T.B. patients --", "start": 401.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "get diagnosed with T.B. before they die.", "start": 404.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "It means that, if you have T.B.,", "start": 408.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "you have more chance that you won't be detected,", "start": 411.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "but will just die from T.B. secondary infections and so on.", "start": 413.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And if, however,", "start": 420.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "you are detected very early, diagnosed early,", "start": 422.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "treatment can start,", "start": 424.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and even in HIV-positives, it makes sense.", "start": 426.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "You can actually cure T.B.,", "start": 429.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "even in HIV-positives.", "start": 431.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "So in our common language, Dutch,", "start": 434.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "the name for T.B.", "start": 437.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "is \"tering,\"", "start": 439.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "which, etymologically,", "start": 441.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "refers to the smell of tar.", "start": 443.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Already the old Chinese", "start": 446.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and the Greek, Hippocrates,", "start": 448.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "have actually published,", "start": 451.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "documented, that T.B. can be diagnosed", "start": 453.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "based on the volatiles", "start": 456.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "exuding from patients.", "start": 458.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "So what we did is we collected some samples --", "start": 461.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "just as a way of testing --", "start": 463.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "from hospitals,", "start": 465.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "trained rats on them", "start": 467.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and see if this works,", "start": 470.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and wonder, well,", "start": 472.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we can reach 89 percent sensitivity,", "start": 474.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "86 percent specificity", "start": 476.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "using multiple rats in a row.", "start": 478.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "This is how it works,", "start": 480.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and really, this is a generic technology.", "start": 483.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "We're talking now explosives, tuberculosis,", "start": 486.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "but can you imagine,", "start": 489.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "you can actually put anything under there.", "start": 491.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "So how does it work?", "start": 493.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "You have a cassette with 10 samples.", "start": 495.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "You put these 10 samples at once in the cage.", "start": 497.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "An animal only needs two hundredths of a second", "start": 500.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to discriminate the scent, so it goes extremely fast.", "start": 502.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Here it's already at the third sample.", "start": 505.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "This is a positive sample.", "start": 508.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "It gets a click sound and comes for the food reward.", "start": 512.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And by doing so, very fast,", "start": 517.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we can have like a second-line opinion", "start": 519.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "to see which patients are positive,", "start": 522.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "which are negative.", "start": 524.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Just as an indication,", "start": 527.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "whereas a microscopist can process", "start": 529.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "40 samples in a day,", "start": 531.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "a rat can process", "start": 533.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the same amount of samples", "start": 535.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in seven minutes only.", "start": 537.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "A cage like this --", "start": 539.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "(Applause)", "start": 541.26, "duration": 5.0}, {"text": "A cage like this -- provided that you have rats,", "start": 546.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and we have now currently", "start": 549.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "25 tuberculosis rats --", "start": 551.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "a cage like this, operating throughout the day,", "start": 553.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "can process 1,680 samples.", "start": 556.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Can you imagine the potential offspring applications --", "start": 561.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "environmental detection", "start": 564.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of pollutants in soils,", "start": 566.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "customs applications,", "start": 568.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "detection of illicit goods in containers and so on.", "start": 570.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "But let's stick first to tuberculosis.", "start": 574.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I just want to briefly highlight,", "start": 576.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the blue rods", "start": 578.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "are the scores of microscopy only", "start": 580.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "at the five clinics in Dar es Salaam", "start": 582.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "on a population of 500,000 people,", "start": 585.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "where 15,000 reported to get a test done.", "start": 587.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Microscopy for 1,800 patients.", "start": 590.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And by just presenting the samples once more to the rats", "start": 593.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "and looping those results back,", "start": 597.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "we were able to increase case detection rates", "start": 600.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "by over 30 percent.", "start": 602.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Throughout last year,", "start": 604.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we've been -- depending on which intervals you take --", "start": 606.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we've been consistently", "start": 608.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "increasing case detection rates", "start": 610.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in five hospitals in Dar es Salaam", "start": 612.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "between 30 and 40 percent.", "start": 614.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "So this is really considerable.", "start": 617.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Knowing that a missed patient by microscopy", "start": 619.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "infects up to 15 people,", "start": 621.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "healthy people, per year,", "start": 623.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "you can be sure", "start": 625.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that we have saved lots of lives.", "start": 627.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "At least our hero rats have saved lots of lives.", "start": 629.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "The way forward for us", "start": 632.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "is now to standardize this technology.", "start": 634.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And there are simple things", "start": 636.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "like, for instance, we have a small laser in the sniffer hole", "start": 638.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "where the animal has to stick for five seconds.", "start": 642.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "So, to standardize this.", "start": 644.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Also, to standardize the pellets,", "start": 646.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the food rewards,", "start": 648.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and to semi-automate this", "start": 650.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in order to replicate this on a much larger scale", "start": 652.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and affect the lives of many more people.", "start": 655.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "To conclude, there are also other applications at the horizon.", "start": 658.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Here is a first prototype", "start": 661.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of our camera rat,", "start": 663.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "which is a rat with a rat backpack", "start": 665.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "with a camera that can go under rubble", "start": 667.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to detect for victims", "start": 669.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "after earthquake and so on.", "start": 671.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "This is in a prototype stage.", "start": 673.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "We don't have a working system here yet.", "start": 675.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "To conclude, I would actually like to say,", "start": 678.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "you may think this is about rats, these projects,", "start": 681.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "but in the end it is about people.", "start": 683.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "It is about empowering vulnerable communities", "start": 685.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to tackle difficult, expensive", "start": 687.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and dangerous humanitarian detection tasks,", "start": 690.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and doing that with a local resource,", "start": 693.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "plenty available.", "start": 696.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "So something completely different", "start": 698.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "is to keep on challenging your perception", "start": 701.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "about the resources surrounding you,", "start": 704.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "whether they are environmental,", "start": 707.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "technological, animal, or human.", "start": 710.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And to respectfully harmonize with them", "start": 715.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "in order to foster a sustainable world.", "start": 718.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Thank you very much.", "start": 721.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "(Applause)", "start": 723.26, "duration": 2.0}]